    <title>在Jfinal中使用JSP视图</title>
    <link href="https://wavevan.github.io/2019/12/19/JFinal-use-JSP/"/>
    <id>https://wavevan.github.io/2019/12/19/JFinal-use-JSP/</id>
    <published>2019-12-18T16:00:34.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-12-20T15:42:12.853Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>因为公司有很多比较小的项目（有时候可能只有一个提交页面)，所以JFinal也是公司主流在使用的一个框架，很大一部分同事都在用。平时我还是喜欢使用Spring系列，今天来了一个小的活动开发，就想用一下JFinal，但是看了文档默认的视图（模版引擎）是自带的Enjoy模版引擎，不想增加学习成本于是就使用原始的JSP来开发。<br><a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="Jfinal版本"><a href="#Jfinal版本" class="headerlink" title="Jfinal版本"></a>Jfinal版本</h2><p>因为3.5及之后版本要求jdk1.8，而我使用的jdk是1.7所以使用此版本。</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span>com.jfinal<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>jfinal<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">version</span>&gt;</span>3.4<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">version</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="使用JSP视图"><a href="#使用JSP视图" class="headerlink" title="使用JSP视图"></a>使用JSP视图</h2><ol><li><p>引入所需jstl相关依赖</p> <figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.apache.taglibs<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>taglibs-standard-spec<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">version</span>&gt;</span>1.2.1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">version</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.apache.taglibs<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>taglibs-standard-impl<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">version</span>&gt;</span>1.2.1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">version</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>设置Jfinal全局视图<br> BaseConfig.java</p> <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//设置全局视图类型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">configConstant</span><span class="params">(Constants me)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">loadConfig();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">me.setDevMode(p.getBoolean(<span class="string">"devMode"</span>, <span class="keyword">false</span>));</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">me.setViewType(ViewType.JSP);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//设置全局视图文件（jsp）位置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">configRoute</span><span class="params">(Routes me)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">me.setBaseViewPath(<span class="string">"/WEB-INF/view"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">me.add(<span class="string">"/"</span>, IndexController.class);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>页面设置</p><p> 完成上上面的配置基本上就可以使用jsp视图了。<br> IndexController.java</p> <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@ActionKey</span>(<span class="string">"/index"</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">index</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">setAttr(<span class="string">"text"</span>, <span class="string">"Hello JSP"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">render(<span class="string">"index.jsp"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> index.jsp(/WEB-INF/view该路径下，上面setBaseViewPath()设置的路径)  </p> <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">%@</span> <span class="attr">page</span> <span class="attr">language</span>=<span class="string">"java"</span> <span class="attr">import</span>=<span class="string">"java.util.*"</span> <span class="attr">pageEncoding</span>=<span class="string">"UTF-8"</span>%&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">%@</span> <span class="attr">taglib</span> <span class="attr">uri</span>=<span class="string">"http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/core"</span> <span class="attr">prefix</span>=<span class="string">"c"</span>%&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">%@</span> <span class="attr">taglib</span> <span class="attr">uri</span>=<span class="string">"http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/fmt"</span> <span class="attr">prefix</span>=<span class="string">"fmt"</span>%&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">%@</span> <span class="attr">taglib</span> <span class="attr">uri</span>=<span class="string">"http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/functions"</span> <span class="attr">prefix</span>=<span class="string">"fn"</span>%&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>Hello World<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>$&#123;text &#125;<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">%=request.getAttribute("text")</span> %&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 效果：</p><h1 id="Hello-World"><a href="#Hello-World" class="headerlink" title="Hello World"></a>Hello World</h1><h2 id="text-Hello-JSP"><a href="#text-Hello-JSP" class="headerlink" title="${text }Hello JSP"></a>${text }Hello JSP</h2><p> el表达式依然没法使用，网上找了下需要在jsp页面在加上一个设置</p> <figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">%@</span> <span class="attr">page</span> <span class="attr">isELIgnored</span>=<span class="string">"false"</span> %&gt;</span>  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">%@</span> <span class="attr">page</span> <span class="attr">language</span>=<span class="string">"java"</span> <span class="attr">import</span>=<span class="string">"java.util.*"</span> <span class="attr">pageEncoding</span>=<span class="string">"UTF-8"</span>%&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">%@</span> <span class="attr">taglib</span> <span class="attr">uri</span>=<span class="string">"http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/core"</span> <span class="attr">prefix</span>=<span class="string">"c"</span>%&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">%@</span> <span class="attr">taglib</span> <span class="attr">uri</span>=<span class="string">"http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/fmt"</span> <span class="attr">prefix</span>=<span class="string">"fmt"</span>%&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">%@</span> <span class="attr">taglib</span> <span class="attr">uri</span>=<span class="string">"http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/functions"</span> <span class="attr">prefix</span>=<span class="string">"fn"</span>%&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>Hello World<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>$&#123;text &#125;<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">%=request.getAttribute("text")</span> %&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 修改之后的效果：</p><h1 id="Hello-World-1"><a href="#Hello-World-1" class="headerlink" title="Hello World"></a>Hello World</h1><h2 id="Hello-JSPHello-JSP"><a href="#Hello-JSPHello-JSP" class="headerlink" title="Hello JSPHello JSP"></a>Hello JSPHello JSP</h2><p> 至此就可以使用JSP进行页面的开发了。</p></li></ol>]]></content>
    
